Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Total resolution time of 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER and the end of the case

Name: Minimun time from 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' to 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Time until 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time it takes 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' to be done after 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Average time it takes from 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' to 'Request Payment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Total time from 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' to 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' in cases of re-submission
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Minimun resolution time of 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' in the process
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total time for 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' in cases leading to 'Payment Handled'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Elapsed time between 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and next 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Average time for 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' to be followed by a 'Declaration FOR_APPROVAL by SUPERVISOR'
